<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">who himself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 held the post of Fullerian Professor of Chemistry at the Royal Institution of Great Britain. 
