<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">who himself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 was the first, and most famous, holder of this position to which 
<REF ID="1654.10" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np-subj">
